Q1 = []
Q2 = []
IQR = []
filter = []
def check_outliers(data):
    global df_wsales
    Q1 = df_wsales['weekly_sales'].quantile(0.25)
    Q3 = df_wsales['weekly_sales'].quantile(0.75)
    IQR = Q3 - Q1  

    filter = (df_wsales['weekly_sales'] >= Q1 - 1.5 * IQR) & (df_wsales['weekly_sales'] <= Q3 + 1.5 *IQR)
#   print(filter)
    df_wsales= df_wsales.loc[filter]
    return df_wsales
